1028:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *
1029:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  Once this function is called to initialize a widget and a sensor, the
1030:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  CapSense_1_CSDScanExt() function is called to scan the sensor.
1031:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *
1032:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  This function is called when no scanning is in progress. I.e.
